videos.description: Lousiville's Deng Adel gets a defensive rebound against George Mason and takes it to the basket for a sweet dunk.
videos.headline: Adel recovers and takes it to the rim

videos.description: George Mason's Jaire Grayer shot is smacked away by Louisville's 7-foot center Anas Mahmoud.
videos.headline: Grayer's layup rejected by Mahmoud

videos.description: Anas Mahmoud recovers Quentin Snider's missed shot and Jordan Nwora hits a 3-pointer. Louisville leads George Mason 57-53 with less than four minutes remaining in the second half.
videos.headline: Mahmoud keeps it alive and Nwora sinks 3
